Steps for Fragmentation in Android : 

1) create the .xml file for fragment as needed.

2) Create the classes for all the .xml file of Fragments.

3) override onCreateView method in that.

4) In .xml file of MainActivity take the <fragment> tag as of many needed.

5) In Class file for MainActivity create FragmentManager, FragmentTransaction and add it using object of FragmentTransaction.



XML Pull Parser : http://www.tutorialspoint.com/android/android_xml_parsers.html

